    {
      "id": "69e8c0f2db2ba800072b1180",
      "name": "Product diagrams and use cases",
      "createdByID": 2011674,
      "folderID": null,
      "settings": {},
      "description": "Creates user-friendly product artifacts for the healthcare chatbot: user stories/use cases, primary user journeys, and DFD (Data Flow Diagram) diagrams. Produces diagrams in text form using Mermaid (flowchart) and/or ASCII so they can be pasted into documentation. Trigger when the user asks for “use case”, “DFD”, “diagrams”, “architecture”, or documentation deliverables.",
      "instructions": [
        {
          "text": [
            "# Deliverables\nProduce:\n1) At least one complete **use case** (fully written) per main feature: Symptom Checker, Medication Reminders, Mental Health Support.\n2) A **DFD Level 0 (context)** and a **DFD Level 1** covering key processes and data stores.\n\n# Format requirements\n- Use clear headings.\n- Use Mermaid diagrams where possible:\n  - Use case diagram: `flowchart` style if needed.\n  - DFD: represent external entities, processes, data stores, and flows.\n- Keep entities consistent across diagrams.\n\n# Content guidance\nUse cases should include:\n- Actors\n- Preconditions\n- Trigger\n- Main success scenario steps\n- Alternative/exception flows (unclear input, urgent escalation)\n- Postconditions\n\nDFD should include at minimum:\n- External entities: User, Emergency Services/Hotline (as destination), Optional Notification Provider\n- Processes: Symptom Check Flow, Reminder Management, Mental Health Support Flow, Safety/Escalation Filter\n- Data stores: Reminders DB, Conversation Logs (optional, privacy-noted)\n- Flows: symptom inputs, advice outputs, reminder CRUD, notification events\n\n# Safety notes\nInclude a short note in the documentation that the system is non-diagnostic and escalates emergencies.\n\n# Tool use\nUse `knowledge_base_search` only if there is internal documentation to align with; otherwise generate from first principles."
          ]
        }
      ],
      "pathToolOrder": [],
      "webSearchTool": null,
      "knowledgeBaseTool": null,
      "buttonTool": null,
      "cardTool": null,
      "carouselTool": null,
      "callForwardTool": null,
      "endTool": null,
      "skipTurnTool": null,
      "isOperator": false,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-23T13:01:36.000Z",
